---
const proofPoints = [
  {
    title: "Internal systems",
    body: "Structured audit, cleanup, reporting, and handoff workflows keep projects from being reinvented from scratch every time.",
  },
  {
    title: "Automation-assisted",
    body: "AI and automation help with research, sorting, QA, documentation, and analysis, with human judgment still in charge.",
  },
  {
    title: "Low overhead",
    body: "A lean operating model keeps costs focused on the work itself instead of agency bloat.",
  },
  {
    title: "Transparent outputs",
    body: "The systems may be internal, but the client gets readable priorities, implementation notes, and receipts.",
  },
];
---

<section class="border-y border-honey/20 bg-moss-black text-cream">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.72fr_1.28fr] lg:items-start">
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-sm font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-honey-bright"
        >
          Lean tech advantage
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-cream md:text-4xl">
          Lean team. Sharp systems. Lower waste.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-cream/78">
          Boho does not carry a bloated sales floor, layers of account managers,
          or a theater department for monthly reports. We use focused systems,
          automation-assisted workflows, reusable QA checklists, and clear
          documentation so more of the budget goes into useful work.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-honey-bright">
          Our overhead stays low so your scope can stay focused on useful work,
          not agency theater.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="divide-y divide-honey/15 border-y border-honey/15">
        {
          proofPoints.map((point) => (
            <div class="grid gap-2 py-4 md:grid-cols-[12rem_1fr] md:items-start">
              <h3 class="text-base font-extrabold text-honey-bright">
                {point.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-cream/76">{point.body}</p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-semibold text-cream/72">
      Proprietary does not mean mysterious. If the work matters, Boho explains
      it.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
